	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The only way to fix it is with a line doubler, and they're usually expensive. I would seriously consider getting another TV or continue to use the old one for progressive consoles if you still have it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


