<br />
<br />In this case, it was a professional "scaler" with 240p to 540p upscaling, with only 4ms delay, and 540p turns off the scaler in my TV as it's a native scanrate, the Zapper worked.
<br />
<br />And yea, the one I borrowed costa  couple grand.

		

