<br />it should, yes.  But I wouldn't trust an LCD.
<br />
<br />They don't make CRT HDTV's anymore, but if you can find one that has a mode that the scaler shuts off (usually 540p and 1080i), you might get away with it.
<br />
<br />I used the "Radiance" scaler, worth a lot of cash, and my friend wouldn't trust me alone with it..  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" />

		

