<br />But anyway, if anyone can borrow the "Lumagen Radiance" scaler, try it on your HDTV with the zapper.
<br />
<br />540p is the same 60Hz as 240p, electrically, and as long as the TV doesn't try to process it, it should work, as in my case.  I used a Prima HT2778P...  (there's two versions of these..  mine doesn't use the red mouse cursor on the OSD)..

		

